{"tid":377052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲首富王健林攜家眷飛英國 天津被禁出境","createTime":"2017-08-27T12:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T13:06:15.000Z","uid":53000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a841ea944305135f595e5da028919dd7ad9c9f7","tid":377052,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"擁近2,000億人民幣資產的中國富豪王健林被禁止出境？海外華文媒體博聞社今日報道，指從天津知情者得悉，王健林前日（25日）攜帶全家到天津機場，準備乘坐私人飛機前住英國時被攔截並扣留，談話數小時後才准許他離開，但被告知禁止出境。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，王健林被限制出境，很可能是其萬達集團的飛速發展，很難擺脫和高層的種種關係。報道引述商界知情者稱，王健林的地產帝國其實早就是負資產，他這幾年加快資本轉移海外，將更多債務留給銀行，等於是坑國家或者納稅人。<br />\n<br />\n樂居網報道，王健林不只賣掉77間萬達酒店給富力地產、13座萬達城給融創中國，連僅剩的「王牌」萬達廣場商城也要賣掉。不同於萬達城、萬達酒店，是打包託售，萬達廣場則是分割出售。其中，南昌西湖萬達廣場7月5日賣給珠江投資、新南方集團和韓建投資等廣東系的珠江人壽保險；而4月中江蘇鹽城的萬達廣場，全部股權已賣給了中信信託。<br />\n<br />\n內地銀監會在今年6月下令，要求各家銀行排查萬達的授信和債務融資風險。分析指出，萬達廣場大幅減資的原因，就是被行政機關勒令減少註冊資本。<br />\n<br />\n不過，博聞社指，目前仍未能聯絡到王健林本人核實此事。"},{"pid":"a6aa812e073459f35e7cf9ed3922596120fd3f1d","tid":377052,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"王思聰之前仲咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5f95395c124c3756f3129942f435e98a6c0633","tid":377052,"uid":34947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王思聰之前仲咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢都好似消失左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8f3b95d9153a6a436e6153022fea5b91821de6","tid":377052,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefd4df03c831542529a0ed23e97d5e334472f30","tid":377052,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:47:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20de79e7579373d7fe3aa6f41037b380d4895781","tid":377052,"uid":9062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:49:43.000Z","msg":"誠哥醒目走得快<br />\n好世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b670f65824caf83f1e01cfe28fa32f5d74793c9d","tid":377052,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"中國人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國夢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d01685ce9e20d3a2b922c2745716992e3d00720","tid":377052,"uid":26601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:06:15.000Z","msg":"誠哥又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}